Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.48,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,彻底唤醒
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,一次次低语
